column67: Participants at the research day can make use of a special registration fee of 450 Euros that covers attendance at both the research day and the  three summit days. It is not possible to register just for the research day.
column141: The best abstracts presented at the research day will be invited to submit full papers to the European Transport Research Review (ETRR), open access Journal published by Springer and created by ECTRI in 2008.
column164: Anyone submitting an abstract who is under 35 years of age can enter the ITF Young Researcher Awards.  ITF presents this award each year , carries a prize of 5000 Euros. The deadline  is 20 February 2018. Details at http://2018.itf-oecd.org/awards
